to\": 6345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lesbians rejoice!\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So you know I am rooting against any team playing our arrogant hoopsters, even though the U.S. has virtually no chance of losing any games.\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Epitomizing the mad times we live in, the obese drag queen who defamed Jesus in the \\\"tribute to Dionysus,\\\" is now threatening to sue all her \\\"right-wing haters.\\\"\", \"from\": 6505, \"to\": 6666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6547, \"end\": 6552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obesity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.14687035696688e-30, \"text\": \"obese\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obesity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obesity\"}, {\"begin\": 6576, \"end\": 6581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999650408433, \"rank\": 3.495948145512716e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 6601, \"end\": 6609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5482165106062428e-34, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is where we are at.\", \"from\": 6667, \"to\": 6691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The insane, allowed to roam free and prosper in a rigged economy that does not work for eighty percent of the people, feel empowered enough to launch lawsuits over anyone daring to criticize them.\", \"from\": 6692, \"to\": 6888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone taking advantage of that whole \\\"racist\\\" First Amendment thing.\", \"from\": 6889, \"to\": 6958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But this does not apply to eccentric \\\"conspiracy theorists,\\\" for example.\", \"from\": 6959, \"to\": 7032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Defame them all you want.\", \"from\": 7033, \"to\": 7058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the things this lovely creature accused her \\\"haters\\\" of is \\\"anti-Semitism.\\\"\", \"from\": 7059, \"to\": 7141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So another person in the limelight proves to be shockingly Jewish.\", \"from\": 7142, \"to\": 7208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe Congress can amend the Antisemitism Awareness Act to include criticism of obese drag queens.\", \"from\": 7209, \"to\": 7307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7215, \"end\": 7223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9999999980018401, \"rank\": 1.994591308263251e-09, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 7289, \"end\": 7294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obesity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.14687035696688e-30, \"text\": \"obese\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obesity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obesity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the Whole Article  Copyright \\u00a9 Donald Jeffries\", \"from\": 7309, \"to\": 7360, \"entities\": []}]}"